NOR) and the QD as an open\nquantum system, the response is driven by the interference experienced by the\nemitter for parallel and perpendicular field orientations. This provides a\nmechanism for control of the emission rate of a QD by a metal nanoparticle\nacross a much wider range of lifetimes than previously understood.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Sep 2021 13:21:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-20"}
